    "Name": "Locura PRW-LCA",
    "Details": "The Locura is the second machine completed under Penelope Centrella's Project Rewrite, built by Firefly Foundry from stolen Word of Blake technology and Sea Fox clantech. A Thumper Cannon provides area-effect artillery capability while a BattleMech Taser offers the rare option to disable opponents without destroying salvage. Three Artemis IV-guided MML 9s carry standard, long range and inferno munitions. A Watchdog CEWS gives it strong electronic warfare coverage across all engagements.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Missiles</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.2</color></b>",
